<paragraph id="016C1165FFE83930EBD2C32EFAE45F6E" blockId="70.[227,1436,1053,1113]" pageId="70" pageNumber="71">Although exhibiting typical soleid features, we judge that the only, two very small specimens from the Piney Point Formation are not appropriate for further description and taxonomic evaluation.</paragraph>
